  _css  : {-<-}forall {iz jz ijz k}{th : iz <= ijz}{ph : jz <= ijz} ->{->-}{both : Tt ov} ->  Cover ov th ph ->  Cover ov {-<-}{ijz = _ - k}{->-}  (th  os)  (ph  os)
  czz   :                                                                                                        Cover ov                               oz        oz
\end{code}
The flag, |ov|,
determines whether \emph{overlap} is permitted: with |tt| for
